<link rel="match" href="border-image-calc-ref.html">
<style>
  #test {
    background-color: redolid red;
    border-image-slice: 10;
    border-image-source: url("support/green_color.png");
    border-image-width: 100px calc(100px) calc(100%) calc(50% + 50px);
    height: 0;
    width: 0;
  }
</style>
<p>Test passes if there is a green 200px times 200px square.</p><p><p><link href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-backgro/css-backgrounds/#border-image-width"><p>
